description: Try our easy to follow Cherry Muffins recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Cherry Muffins Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Beat butter with electric beaters until pale and creamy. Add icing sugar and beat until smooth. Spread over cooled muffins and decorate with pieces of glacé cherry to represent Christmas holly.
